## Requirements

- Raspberry Pi OS
- Python 3.13+
- SvxLink
- Git

---

## Installation

Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone git@github.com:IU5HJU/svxguardian.git
cd svxguardian
```

Create the virtual environment:

```bash
python3 -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
```

Install dependencies:

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

Run the application:

```bash
python src/main.py
```

---

